1. Selector

      /*Element*/
      li {

      }
      /*class*/
      .hello {

      }
      /*id*/
      #name {

      }

      /*Star - every single element*/

      * {
        border: 1px solid lightgrey;
      }

      /*Descendant Selector for all child, and then div.section > div for just direct child*/

      li a {
        color: red;
      }

      /*Adjacent Selector ul next to h4*/

      h4 + ul {
        border: 4px solid red;
      }


      /*Attribute Selector*/

      a[href="http://www.google.com"] {
        background: blue;
      }

      /*nth of type*/

      li:nth-of-type(odd){
        background: purple;
      }
2. Specificity
ID> class, attribute, psudeo selector> tag selector
